               <msContents class="#MTM">
                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Taṇṭalaiyār Catakam</title>, also known as <title xml:lang="ta">Paḻamoḻi Viḷakkam</title>. This work is attributed to <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Cāntaliṅka Kavirāyar</persName> (Zvelebil 1995, p. 119, 536) and, alternatively, to <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Pātikkācup Pulavar</persName> (Zvelebil 1995, p. 535).</p>

<p>The <foreign xml:lang="ta">Avaiyaṭakkam</foreign> is found twice (U2, f[1]v and U3, f1v).</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (May 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> </summary>
                  
